text: "Something to Talk About" is a 1991 song by Bonnie Raitt from her 11th studio album Luck of the Draw. It went to number 3 in Canada, number 5 in the United States, number 33 in New Zealand, number 57 in Australia and Germany and number 59 in the Netherlands. It won a Grammy Award in 1992. ==References== Category:1991 songs Category:Bonnie Raitt songs Category:Britney Spears songs
